Package swinghelper

Annotation Type GenerationSettings

@Retention(RUNTIME)
@Target({METHOD,TYPE})
public @interface GenerationSettings
Allows to easily generate an JFrame with the specified properties as generated (the dummy JFrame)
You can only attach this to a class or the merge method of a SwingMerger.
Author:
NumericPrime
